{"word":"H4394 - מִלֻּא - milluʼ - mil-loo' - Consecration","slug":"H4394","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִלֻּא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>milluʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mil-loo'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consecration"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05DC;&#x05BC;&#x05D0; - millu&#x0302;'</b> - <i>mil-loo'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H4390\">H4390</a>; a <i>fulfilling</i> (only in plural), that is, (literally) a <i>setting</i> (of gems), or (technically) <i>consecration</i> (also concretely a dedicatory <i>sacrifice</i>): - consecration, be set."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1037\">H1037</a>, <a href=\"#/H3229\">H3229</a>, <a href=\"#/H4390\">H4390</a>, <a href=\"#/H4392\">H4392</a>, <a href=\"#/H4393\">H4393</a>, <a href=\"#/H4395\">H4395</a>, <a href=\"#/H4396\">H4396</a>, <a href=\"#/H4402\">H4402</a>, <a href=\"#/H4407\">H4407</a>"}]}